  "body": "<p>Finally!! The <a href=\"http://bit.ly/WUIXxn\">Yes, Please collection is online at Two Peas In A Bucket</a> ! So thrilled to have this in stores.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600125700378-AZ6EMV1T49Y4Q36VZUUC/15a-DSC_1152-600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139089-authentic-yes-please-amy-tangerine-phrase-roller-stamp/%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">Roller phrase stamp</a> (has a date slot included)</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600125722978-FKSZD5STZI7K1II70WS3/15b-DSC_1155-600x589.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://classic.avantlink.com/click.php?mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;tt=cl&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twopeasinabucket.com%2Fshop%2Famerican-crafts%2F139072-life-yes-please-amy-tangerine-sticker-book%2F%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">Translucent alphabet stickers</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600125763779-3FFM53VHZNK88HRRJDPA/15c-DSC_1158-600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The highly anticipated <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139088-lovely-yes-please-amy-tangerine-calendar-stamp-set/%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">calendar stam</a>p || clouds and sunshine from the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139091-capture-yes-please-amy-tangerine-embroidery-stencil-kit/%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">embroidery stencil kit</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600125792840-U5RCNRRYYB2EQVCT7AI1/15d-DSC_1161-600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Feather from the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139091-capture-yes-please-amy-tangerine-embroidery-stencil-kit/%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">embroidery stencil kit</a> || <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139087-document-yes-please-amy-tangerine-alphabet-stamp-set/%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">wood alphabet stamps</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600125812043-B5YQTQ5OD5VYE1L5TG25/15e-Yes-Please1.png\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>You all have been so wonderful with all of your kind comments about the line. Now I can't wait to see what you make with it! Shop the entire <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_yes_please_/%3Fpp%3D300\">Yes, Please collection at Two Peas In a Bucket</a></p>"
